name: Hire budget SUV with five seats for one week trip -- @1.1

steps.name: Given user is on budget application home page
When user types "aus" and selects pickup and return location as "Austin Bergstrom Intl Airport"
And pickup date as week ahead of current date
And return date as week ahead of pickup date
And clicks Select My car option to navigate to reservations page
And chooses lowest price SUV with "4" doors and "5" seats and click pay now option
Then user validates base rate, fees and taxes and estimated prepaid total succesfully
